==History==
*This spell was added in [[0.32]]. An earlier revision of this was a level 7 Alchemy/Earth spell known as '''Seismic Cannonade'''. More information on this earlier version can be found [http://crawl.chaosforge.org/index.php?title=Seismic_Cannonade&oldid=80317 here] and [http://crawl.chaosforge.org/index.php?title=Seismic_cannon&oldid=80322 here].
